name: My migratory bird
description:
From the collection: "Inside: Missing thongs"

I stayed in your smile
And something in me went with you
Like flowers that will go with spring
And migratory birds
Something exclusive inside me, crawled in your suitcase
And miles
And miles
And miles
walked away from me
And never returned…
Like that smile that sat on my lips with you
And the feeling in my heart
When I was in your arms
Something like beauty
And youth
And light
And green colors 
Something which never returned
not with springs 
not with migratory birds 
not even with you ...
